# Mainnet Keypair Storage
# ========================
# 
# This directory stores mainnet keypairs.
# NEVER COMMIT ACTUAL KEYPAIR FILES TO VERSION CONTROL!
#
# Required files for mainnet deployment:
# - mint-authority.json    (controls wVRTY minting)
# - freeze-authority.json  (compliance freeze capability)
# - treasury-authority.json (bridge treasury control)
#
# Generate keypairs securely using:
#   solana-keygen new --outfile mint-authority.json
#
# For production, consider:
# - Hardware wallet (Ledger)
# - HSM (Hardware Security Module)
# - Multi-sig setup
#
# Security checklist:
# [ ] Keypairs generated on air-gapped machine
# [ ] Private keys stored in encrypted vault
# [ ] Backup copies in secure cold storage
# [ ] Access logged and audited
